transcript.text:
One story is about this baby,
and his name is Odin. His father was a blogger. And he was writing his blog one day, and his wife gave birth to her baby at 25 weeks. And he never expected this. One day, it was normal;
the next day, it was hell. And this is a one-pound baby. So Odin was documented every single day.

